This repository showcases a collection of Power BI projects built using real-world datasets. Each project demonstrates the complete Business Intelligence workflow—from data preparation and modeling to visualization and actionable business insights.

---

 🚀 About This Repository

The projects in this repository are designed to solve real business problems using Power BI.

They demonstrate my ability to:

- Transform raw data into interactive dashboards
- Design efficient data models
- Create powerful DAX measures
- Build business KPIs
- Develop insightful visualizations
- Support data-driven decision-making
- Tell compelling stories with data

