 📂 Projects Included

 📈 Hr Dashboard

Analyze business performance through:

- Attrition count by department 
- Attrition trend by years at company 
- Job Role × Job Satisfaction pivot table
- Attrition by education field 
- Attrition vs. salary hike 
- Attrition by job level 

---

🛒 BlinkIT Grocery Sales Dashboard

Business Intelligence dashboard focusing on:

- Grocery Sales Performance
- Product Categories
- Outlet Analysis
- Customer Ratings
- Inventory Insights
- Sales Trends

---

🌍 Global Layoffs Dashboard

Interactive dashboard analyzing worldwide layoffs.

Key analyses include:

- Layoffs by Country
- Layoffs by Industry
- Company Performance
- Monthly Trends
- Economic Impact

