---

 🎯 Why Power BI?

Power BI is one of the leading Business Intelligence platforms that enables organizations to:

- Visualize complex data
- Monitor KPIs
- Track business performance
- Discover trends
- Improve decision-making
- Share interactive reports across teams

This repository demonstrates how Power BI can transform data into valuable business insights.

